node.text:
Its always horrible when you dont know whats wrong with your pet and they are not 100% but im putting her sickness down to eating too many bugs from the previous night. There was alot of daddy long legs in the house and throughout the night i heard her chirping away chasing them so i suspect she has caught and eaten her fair share of them. 
Thankfully she was back to her usual self this morning ❤
